"""
        Make sure all expected components of vocabulary are initialized
        """
self.assertEqual(type(self.con.vocab), cv.Vocabulary)
for item in [self.con.vocab.vocabularies, self.con.vocab.suggested, self.
    con.vocab.all_codes, self.con.vocab.code_types, self.con.vocab.methods,
    self.con.vocab.age_methods]:
    self.assertTrue(len(item))
